{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban AI generated videos being posted on steaming services for children",
        "additional_details": "This should be banned because unregulated AI-generated content marketed as child-friendly can expose children to inappropriate themes, disturbing imagery, misinformation, and unsafe messages. We are concerned that platforms are placing low-quality AI videos in kids\u2019 sections without proper oversight, prioritizing volume and clicks over child safety and developmental standards.",
        "background": "Ban the upload or distribution of AI-generated content that is marketed as child-friendly without proper review and regulation. We are concerned that unregulated, low-quality AI material is appearing on platforms and being placed in children\u2019s sections, where much of it is inappropriate for children",
